                  {
                    "id": "blk_104",
                    "type": "content",
                    "title": "Stay Calm and Listen",
                    "body": "When a customer has a complaint, remain calm and professional. Let them express their concern fully without interrupting. Show empathy by acknowledging their feelings with phrases like 'I understand your frustration' or 'I apologize for the inconvenience.'"
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "blk_105",
