                    "type": "content",
                    "title": "Offer Solutions",
                    "body": "After listening, offer concrete solutions. If you can't resolve the issue immediately, explain what steps you'll take and give a realistic timeframe. Always follow through on your promises. If needed, escalate to a supervisor while staying with the customer."
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
